  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>C&#43;&#43;</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Check For</h1>\n  <p>Verify that deallocation functions don't throw exceptions.</p>\n  <h1>Why</h1>\n  <p>Deallocation functions may be called when exceptions are thrown. If a deallocation function throws an exception after being called when an exception is thrown, the program may terminate. This may result in a denial-of-service vulnerability.</p>\n  <h1>How to Check</h1>\n  <p>Search for deallocation functions. Verify that deallocation functions don't throw exceptions.</p>\n  <h1>How to Fix</h1>\n  <p>Identify deallocation functions that throw exceptions and rewrite them in such a way that they don't throw exceptions.</p>\n  <h1>Additional Resources</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>For more information about not throwing exceptions from deallocation functions, please see <a href=\"https://www.securecoding.cert.org/confluence/display/cplusplus/ERR38-CPP.&#43;Deallocation&#43;functions&#43;must&#43;not&#43;throw&#43;exceptions\">https://www.securecoding.cert.org/confluence/display/cplusplus/ERR38-CPP.&#43;Deallocation&#43;functions&#43;must&#43;not&#43;throw&#43;exceptions</a></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>Related Items</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>\n      <a href=\"/article/441b4138-1866-442f-8abb-6d05236d6fcb\">Don't Throw Exceptions from Deallocation Functions</a>\n      <li>\n        <a href=\"/article/fd06b089-88ea-43df-bc41-f111a1848116\">Don't Throw Exceptions from Destructors</a>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"/article/2e732e9d-5677-40cc-8e33-c40ceacc056b\">\n            <a href=\"/article/2e732e9d-5677-40cc-8e33-c40ceacc056b\">Destructors don't throw exceptions</a>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n      </li>\n    </li>\n  </ul>"
